description: The McDonnell F2H-3 Banshee is a carrier-capable all-weather interceptor, fighter-bomber, and tactical nuclear bomber. It is a major development of the F2H-2 with a lengthened fuselage, increased fuel capacity, additional weapon stations, and the APQ-41 search radar. This variant has an air-to-air refueling probe fitted in place of the upper port cannon.
